creator: Battersea Power Station Development Company
descriptionHtml:
This is the start of a new digital experience of life at Battersea Power Station and your app is here to help you enjoy every moment. Here’s a flavour of what The Power Club app can do for you as a resident - on your doorstep and away from it all:

· Join an exclusive online community
· Safely and securely chat and connect with neighbours
· Create and join groups and local community events
· Send and receive messages with your concierge at Concierge Plus, ready to help wherever you are in the world
· Book events at Battersea Power Station and elsewhere
· Book resident services including dining, seats at the Screening Room and more
· Receive alerts from your concierge of any packages or deliveries you’re expecting
· View your apartment details
· Read the latest community news and announcements
